</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_13" id="6r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_13_r3l28"><expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> wılhelmſtorffer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r3l29">cʒu vvılhelmſtorff geſeſſen </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_13_r3l30"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> VVılhelmſtorffer vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> C <expan>wernh<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vvıe daʒ Er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r3l31">nü newlıch als Er von wınſheim herauff füre <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> armmanne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r3l32">cʒu neitharſwinde v̈ber <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> abgeſnẏten acker gefaren ſeẏ / Darümb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r3l33">Jn der ewr angefallen vnd Jn gewundet / vnd Jn auch <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r3l34">bekümert hab v̈ber das / daʒ Er <expan>gepote<ex>n</ex></expan> hab / het Er Jm icht ſchadens </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r3l35">getan / ſo vvolt Er Jm das puſſen als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das reht darümb erkante </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r3l36">das vns von ~ <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> vnglımpflich dunckt <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> ~ ew<gap reason="damaged"/></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r3l37"><expan>ſchıcke<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beſtelle<ex>n</ex></expan> vvöllet / daʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ledig vverde / <gap reason="damaged"/></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r3l38"><expan>vvölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc / <expan>Antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ṽ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>nat<ex>ivitatia</ex></expan> <expan>b<ex>ea</ex>te</expan> <expan>Ma<ex>r</ex>ıe</expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_13" id="6r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> Wilhelmstorffer, czu Wilhelmstorff gesessen
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Wilhelmstorffer, uns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
<expan>C<ex>huncz</ex></expan>
<expan>Wernh<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz er nü newlich, als er von Winsheim herauff füre,
                <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> armmanne czu Neitharswinde über
              <expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan> abgesnyten acker gefaren sey, darümb in der ewr
            angefallen und in gewundet und in auch <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> und bekümert
            hab über das, daz er <expan>gepote<ex>n</ex></expan> hab; het er im icht schadens getan,
            so wolt er im das pussen, als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> das reht darümb erkante, das
            uns von <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> unglimpflich dunckt. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz
            ir mit <expan>de<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>rn</ex></expan> <expan>schicke<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                <expan>bestelle<ex>n</ex></expan> wöllet, daz der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> ledig werde <app>
<note><gap reason="damaged"/></note>
</app>
<expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> v <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>nat<ex>ivitatia</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ea</ex>te</expan>
<expan>Ma<ex>r</ex>ie</expan>. </ab></div>
